name: Experiment Or Die #117
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Peeking out from the storm, get a head start on the night even if it's just a few mins, and maybe just maybe I'd say I'm caught up...if it weren't for the airdrops that I need to catch up on also! Baby steps but headed in the right direction! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
